<hw>deaf-mutism</hw></mhw> <pos>n.</pos>
<def>the condition of being a deaf-mute; a congenital deafness that
results in inability to speak.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

